title: 845 Picnic Time Colby
transcripts: The Colby by Picnic Time is a combination cheeseboard and serving tray with a hidden pull out drawer and a recessed borrow fro serving crackers. The board is made of eco-friendly rubber wood. It has a groove along the top edges to collect brine or juice from soft cheeses olives of cut fruits. The Colby's innovative design features a drawer that pulls out from the tray and houses three stainless steel cheese tools with rubber wood handles. These include a serrated cheese spreading knife, a cheese fork, and a hard cheese knife. compact and ready to use in a moment. The Colby makes a delightful gift for people who enjoy entertaining either at home or away.
